trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Moses Lake
There were no other sightings in Moses Lake on or around August 18th 2008
divs: Sighting Detailsi was at my friends house spending the night, and we sleep on his trampoline. we also had a third person there. we were talking for a long time, just about stuff, when we heard a weird whirrring noise and two missle like things flew overhead. all three of us heard and saw these two things. as they flew across they shimmered slightly. they also flew very low to the ground, we thought they were about to hit the other house. my friend thought it was a remote control helicopter, but we pointed out to him that they dont fly that fast. later he said that he said that only because he was afraid. it took us a long while to go to sleep. they just flew off out of sight. and we were all really startled.
